net.ponec.jworksheet.bo
Class Event

java.lang.Object
  org.ujoframework.extensions.AbstractUjo
      org.ujoframework.implementation.bean.BeanUjo
          net.ponec.jworksheet.bo.Event
All Implemented Interfaces:
UjoCloneable, UjoTextable, Ujo
public class Event
extends BeanUjo

An Event of the Work Day. I have selected the BeanUjo implementaton for its small memory footprint, two fields are stored in a memory safe data type in addition:

  • time - primitive short
  • description - byte array in a UTF format
